[code=vb]Private Sub WebBrowser1_BeforeNavigate2(ByVal pDisp As Object, URL As Variant, flags As Variant, TargetFrameName As Variant, PostData As Variant, Headers As Variant, Cancel As Boolean) On Error Resume Next If URL = "http://www.runescape.com/" Then Cancel = True End Sub[/code]

[code=vb]Private Sub Command57_Click() If Text2.Text = "1" Then WebBrowser1.Navigate "http://ul2.runescape.com/lang/en/aff/runescape/game.ws?lowmem=1&plugin=0" End If If Text2.Text = "2" Then 'This makes a integer and a world variable to use for the detail and world
Dim intDetail As Integer = "0" 
Dim strWorld As Single = ""

'If the "High Detail" Checkbox is checked then will switch to highdetail
